attributes.Long form description: The student's task is to assemble the KNARREVIK. So, he starts by screwing each of the four legs to the shelf, then, the student aligns and inserts the tabletop in between the four legs so that then he can screw the legs to the tabletop to complete the task.

attributes.Transcription: Great, now we are going to look at this furniture.

attributes.Transcription: You should start by placing one of the shelf vertically on the table, the larger side on the table.
And then try to fix one of the feet on this shelf. This shelf is going to be the middle shelf. So the foot should be aligned with the middle holes.
